Detailed Description

Field Documentation

Vps_M2mDssInPipeParams Vps_M2mDssParams::inPipePrms[VPS_DSS_DISPC_PIPE_MAX]

Input pipe parameters. User should set this as per the number of input pipes configured at create time.

Vps_M2mDssOutPipeParams Vps_M2mDssParams::outPipePrms

WB output parameters.

Vps_DssDispcOvlyPanelConfig Vps_M2mDssParams::ovlyCfg

Overlay configuration applicable only when WB is captured from an overlay. Otherwise set this to default values.

UInt32 Vps_M2mDssParams::ovlyHeight

Height of overlay when WB is captured from an overlay. Otherwise this is not applicable and can be set to zero.

UInt32 Vps_M2mDssParams::ovlyWidth

Width of overlay when WB is captured from an overlay. Otherwise this is not applicable and can be set to zero.
